{"type":"message","id":"6a677bac","parentId":"050c7a2b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T23:48:06.782Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e56d27b6927e410f98a0a314","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Your AI assistant, now without the $3,499 headset.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron edit [options] <id>\n\nEdit a cron job (patch fields)\n\nArguments:\n  id                                   Job id\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>                       Channel account id for delivery\n                                       (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>                         Set agent id\n  --announce                           Announce summary to a chat\n                                       (subagent-style)\n  --at <when>                          Set one-shot time (ISO) or duration like\n                                       20m\n  --best-effort-deliver                Do not fail job if delivery fails\n  --channel <channel>                  Delivery channel (last)\n  --clear-agent                        Unset agent and use default (default:\n                                       false)\n  --clear-session-key                  Unset session key (default: false)\n  --cron <expr>                        Set cron expression\n  --delete-after-run                   Delete one-shot job after it succeeds\n                                       (default: false)\n  --deliver                            Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a\n                                       summary to a chat.\n  --description <text>                 Set description\n  --disable                            Disable job (default: false)\n  --enable                             Enable job (default: false)\n  --every <duration>                   Set interval duration like 10m\n  --exact                              Disable cron staggering (set stagger to\n                                       0)\n  --expect-final                       Wait for final response (agent) (default:\n                                       false)\n  --failure-alert                      Enable failure alerts for this job\n  --failure-alert-account-id <id>      Account ID for failure alert channel\n                                       (multi-account setups)\n  --failure-alert-after <n>            Alert after N consecutive job errors\n  --failure-alert-channel <channel>    Failure alert channel (last)\n  --failure-alert-cooldown <duration>  Minimum time between alerts (e.g. 1h,\n                                       30m)\n  --failure-alert-mode <mode>          Failure alert delivery mode (announce or\n                                       webhook)\n  --failure-alert-to <dest>            Failure alert destination\n  -h, --help                           Display help for command\n  --keep-after-run                     Keep one-shot job after it succeeds\n                                       (default: false)\n  --light-context                      Enable lightweight bootstrap context for\n                                       agent jobs\n  --message <text>                     Set agentTurn payload message\n  --model <model>                      Model override for agent jobs\n  --name <name>                        Set name\n  --no-best-effort-deliver             Fail job when delivery fails\n  --no-deliver                         Disable announce delivery\n  --no-failure-alert                   Disable failure alerts for this job\n  --no-light-context                   Disable lightweight bootstrap context for\n                                       agent jobs\n  --session <target>                   Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>                  Set session key for job routing\n  --stagger <duration>                 Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>                Set systemEvent payload\n  --thinking <level>                   Thinking level for agent jobs\n                                       (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>                       Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>                Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>                          Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram\n                                       chatId, or Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>                      Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>                          Timezone for cron expressions (IANA)\n  --url <url>                          Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to\n                                       gateway.remote.url when configured)\n  --wake <mode>                        Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1476,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.24 (cff6dc9) — Your AI assistant, now without the $3,499 headset.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron edit [options] <id>\n\nEdit a cron job (patch fields)\n\nArguments:\n  id                                   Job id\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>                       Channel account id for delivery\n                                       (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>                         Set agent id\n  --announce                           Announce summary to a chat\n                                       (subagent-style)\n  --at <when>                          Set one-shot time (ISO) or duration like\n                                       20m\n  --best-effort-deliver                Do not fail job if delivery fails\n  --channel <channel>                  Delivery channel (last)\n  --clear-agent                        Unset agent and use default (default:\n                                       false)\n  --clear-session-key                  Unset session key (default: false)\n  --cron <expr>                        Set cron expression\n  --delete-after-run                   Delete one-shot job after it succeeds\n                                       (default: false)\n  --deliver                            Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a\n                                       summary to a chat.\n  --description <text>                 Set description\n  --disable                            Disable job (default: false)\n  --enable                             Enable job (default: false)\n  --every <duration>                   Set interval duration like 10m\n  --exact                              Disable cron staggering (set stagger to\n                                       0)\n  --expect-final                       Wait for final response (agent) (default:\n                                       false)\n  --failure-alert                      Enable failure alerts for this job\n  --failure-alert-account-id <id>      Account ID for failure alert channel\n                                       (multi-account setups)\n  --failure-alert-after <n>            Alert after N consecutive job errors\n  --failure-alert-channel <channel>    Failure alert channel (last)\n  --failure-alert-cooldown <duration>  Minimum time between alerts (e.g. 1h,\n                                       30m)\n  --failure-alert-mode <mode>          Failure alert delivery mode (announce or\n                                       webhook)\n  --failure-alert-to <dest>            Failure alert destination\n  -h, --help                           Display help for command\n  --keep-after-run                     Keep one-shot job after it succeeds\n                                       (default: false)\n  --light-context                      Enable lightweight bootstrap context for\n                                       agent jobs\n  --message <text>                     Set agentTurn payload message\n  --model <model>                      Model override for agent jobs\n  --name <name>                        Set name\n  --no-best-effort-deliver             Fail job when delivery fails\n  --no-deliver                         Disable announce delivery\n  --no-failure-alert                   Disable failure alerts for this job\n  --no-light-context                   Disable lightweight bootstrap context for\n                                       agent jobs\n  --session <target>                   Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>                  Set session key for job routing\n  --stagger <duration>                 Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>                Set systemEvent payload\n  --thinking <level>                   Thinking level for agent jobs\n                                       (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>                       Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>                Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>                          Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram\n                                       chatId, or Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>                      Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>                          Timezone for cron expressions (IANA)\n  --url <url>                          Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to\n                                       gateway.remote.url when configured)\n  --wake <mode>                        Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774914486780}}
