{"type":"message","id":"d42b606a","parentId":"10d2bb89","timestamp":"2026-03-31T00:38:55.094Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5385372a64a4c4f8a8e235a2461\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 08:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5385372a64a4c4f8a8e235a2461]\nou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e:  还有个问题:\n📰 中国7nm芯片再破局，第二家企业现身\n中国半导体行业在7nm工艺取得新突破，第二家企业成功量产7nm芯片。外媒评论称美国禁令已从\"封锁\"变成\"倒逼\"，推动中国建立完全自主的半导体生态。\n🔗 来源：半导体行业观察 | http://www.baidu.com/link\n\n这个链接无效，无法查看，请解决，并记录问题原因和解决方案"}],"timestamp":1774917535090}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff6da308","parentId":"d42b606a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T00:39:09.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户指出了另一个问题：百度搜索结果中的链接是 `http://www.baidu.com/link` 这种短链接，不是真正的原始链接。这些链接需要展开才能获取到真正的源链接。\n\n问题原因：\n- 从百度搜索结果获取的链接是百度的跳转链接（如 `http://www.baidu.com/link?url=xxx`）\n- 这些链接不能直接作为新闻来源链接\n- 需要访问这些链接获取真正的目标 URL\n\n解决方案：\n1. 使用 web_fetch 访问百度链接，获取最终跳转的真实 URL\n2. 或者直接搜索原始标题，找到真正的新闻来源网站\n\n让我先解决这个具体问题，然后更新记忆文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"您说得对！百度搜索结果中的链接是跳转链接，不是真正的源链接。让我修复这个问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7de88ad8fe3846e19c329fdf","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"中国7nm芯片 第二家企业 突破 2026年3月"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":96538,"output":329,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96867,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774917535095,"responseId":"eca816782bde59cab166023b9be4daf8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"da949825","parentId":"ff6da308","timestamp":"2026-03-31T00:39:11.308Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7de88ad8fe3846e19c329fdf","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"中国7nm芯片 第二家企业 突破 2026年3月\",\n  \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1562,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fdd117aa5c622992\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nExclusive: China's No. 2 chipmaker readies 7 nm production as ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fdd117aa5c622992\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-no-2-chipmaker-readies-7-nm-production-beijing-ramps-up-self-suffiency-2026-03-16/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"daf913b7058bd103\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSINGAPORE, March 16 (Reuters) - China's Hua Hong Group has developed advanced chip manufacturing technologies that can be used to produce artificial intelligence chips, four people familiar with the matter said, a major milestone in Beijing's efforts to boost tech self-sufficiency. China's largest contract chipmaker, SMIC (0981.HK), opens new tab, is at present the only domestic producer capable of making chips with 7 nm technologies. Hua Hong Group, Huali, its sister company Hua Hong Semiconductor (688347.SS), opens new tab, and Huawei did not respond to requests for comment. Huali's ‌research ⁠and development on 7 nm chips at its Hua Hong Fab 6 began last year, with support from domestic equipment suppliers including Huawei-backed SiCarrier, which tested its equipment at a facility in Shenzhen last year, a separate source said. Chinese graphics processing unit designer Biren (6082.HK), opens new tab is using Huali's 7 nm ​line for tape-out, ⁠a process in which a chip design is committed to a physical prototype for testing before mass production begins, one of the sources said.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"daf913b7058bd103\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.99991965\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"12755e589d033324\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n中国大陆第二家，突破7nm制程 - 电子工程专辑\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"12755e589d033324\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.eet-china.com/mp/a480965.html\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"55875a5727938e11\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n两位消息人士表示，HLW计划在2026年底前实现7纳米芯片月产能数千片的初期量产规模，并规划后续进一步提升产能。据称，壁仞科技正采用HLW的7纳米产线进行Tape-\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"55875a5727938e11\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9999083\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e035f7006d69b630\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n搞定7nm芯片制造，中国大陆第二家？美国封锁真成废纸了 - 网易\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e035f7006d69b630\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KO7V0CNG0556DKZT.html\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8f1f46b3b268123a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n你看看数据就明白了——2025年，中芯国际的产线利用率超过95%，晶合集成也破了103%。这些数字啥概念？就是机器都快冒烟了，订单还堆成山。尤其是先进芯片这块，\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8f1f46b3b268123a\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.99984527\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4ea0b0cc006082cf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n全球仅4家企业，能制造7nm芯片，2家在中国！但中国或要再多1家了\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4ea0b0cc006082cf\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://m.sohu.com/a/1002509318_121097259?scm=thor.521_14-200000.0.0-0-0-0-0.\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4d2d2d42f392405a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n一家是中国台湾省的台积电，全球最大的芯片代工厂，早在2018年就量产了7nm芯片，目前的技术已经达到了2nm的水平，全球份额最高。\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4d2d2d42f392405a\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9987356\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d5b6ba58b0610160\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nA+H上市国产芯片企业增至7家 - 新浪财经\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d5b6ba58b0610160\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/relnews/cn/2026-03-24/doc-inhsarqt3404133.shtml\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"70c7900a532df3da\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n国际电子商情24日讯 2026年3月23日，国民技术股份有限公司正式在香港联合交易所主板挂牌上市，股票代码为02701.HK。此次上市标志着公司完成了“A+H”两地资本\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"70c7900a532df3da\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9986541\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"中国7nm芯片 第二家企业 突破 2026年3月","provider":"tavily","count":5,"tookMs":1562,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"tavily","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fdd117aa5c622992\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nExclusive: China's No. 2 chipmaker readies 7 nm production as ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fdd117aa5c622992\">>>","url":"https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-no-2-chipmaker-readies-7-nm-production-beijing-ramps-up-self-suffiency-2026-03-16/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"daf913b7058bd103\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSINGAPORE, March 16 (Reuters) - China's Hua Hong Group has developed advanced chip manufacturing technologies that can be used to produce artificial intelligence chips, four people familiar with the matter said, a major milestone in Beijing's efforts to boost tech self-sufficiency. China's largest contract chipmaker, SMIC (0981.HK), opens new tab, is at present the only domestic producer capable of making chips with 7 nm technologies. Hua Hong Group, Huali, its sister company Hua Hong Semiconductor (688347.SS), opens new tab, and Huawei did not respond to requests for comment. Huali's ‌research ⁠and development on 7 nm chips at its Hua Hong Fab 6 began last year, with support from domestic equipment suppliers including Huawei-backed SiCarrier, which tested its equipment at a facility in Shenzhen last year, a separate source said. Chinese graphics processing unit designer Biren (6082.HK), opens new tab is using Huali's 7 nm ​line for tape-out, ⁠a process in which a chip design is committed to a physical prototype for testing before mass production begins, one of the sources said.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"daf913b7058bd103\">>>","score":0.99991965},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"12755e589d033324\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n中国大陆第二家，突破7nm制程 - 电子工程专辑\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"12755e589d033324\">>>","url":"https://www.eet-china.com/mp/a480965.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"55875a5727938e11\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n两位消息人士表示，HLW计划在2026年底前实现7纳米芯片月产能数千片的初期量产规模，并规划后续进一步提升产能。据称，壁仞科技正采用HLW的7纳米产线进行Tape-\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"55875a5727938e11\">>>","score":0.9999083},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e035f7006d69b630\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n搞定7nm芯片制造，中国大陆第二家？美国封锁真成废纸了 - 网易\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e035f7006d69b630\">>>","url":"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KO7V0CNG0556DKZT.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8f1f46b3b268123a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n你看看数据就明白了——2025年，中芯国际的产线利用率超过95%，晶合集成也破了103%。这些数字啥概念？就是机器都快冒烟了，订单还堆成山。尤其是先进芯片这块，\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8f1f46b3b268123a\">>>","score":0.99984527},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4ea0b0cc006082cf\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n全球仅4家企业，能制造7nm芯片，2家在中国！但中国或要再多1家了\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4ea0b0cc006082cf\">>>","url":"https://m.sohu.com/a/1002509318_121097259?scm=thor.521_14-200000.0.0-0-0-0-0.","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4d2d2d42f392405a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n一家是中国台湾省的台积电，全球最大的芯片代工厂，早在2018年就量产了7nm芯片，目前的技术已经达到了2nm的水平，全球份额最高。\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4d2d2d42f392405a\">>>"