{"type":"message","id":"476fcca7","parentId":"1638ae51","timestamp":"2026-03-31T00:39:30.973Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a97abbaf95164ce58c225b1e","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\shared_global_memory.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n   7 ---\n   8 \n   9 ## 🚨 严重错误警示 - 必读\n  10 \n- 11 ### ⚠️ 飞书文档操作两大错误（2026-03-31）\n+ 11 ### ⚠️ 飞书文档操作三大错误（2026-03-31）\n  12 \n- 13 > **这是两次严重错误的记录，所有 agent 必须牢记！**\n+ 13 > **这是三次严重错误的记录，所有 agent 必须牢记！**\n  14 \n  15 ---\n  16 \n  17 #### ❌ 错误一：文档内容为空\n     ...","firstChangedLine":11},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774917570969}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd26f45b","parentId":"476fcca7","timestamp":"2026-03-31T00:39:48.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要添加第三个错误到记忆文件中。让我找到正确的位置插入。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a18721c3807b433790403786","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"🔗 来源：腾讯新闻 | https://view.inews.qq.com/a/20260329A02RIQ00\n```\n\n---\n\n#### ❌ 错误三：使用百度跳转链接而非真正的源链接\n\n**现象：** 新闻链接显示为 `http://www.baidu.com/link...`，无法访问\n\n**根因：** 百度搜索结果中的链接是**跳转链接**，不是真正的源 URL\n\n**为什么这是问题：**\n- 百度链接格式：`http://www.baidu.com/link?url=xxx`\n- 这是百度的跳转服务器，用户点击后才能跳转到真实网站\n- 直接访问这个链接可能失败或显示错误\n\n**必须这样做：**\n```\n❌ 错误链接：\n🔗 来源：半导体行业观察 | http://www.baidu.com/link?url=xxx\n\n✅ 正确链接：\n🔗 来源：Reuters（路透社）| https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-no-2-chipmaker-readies-7-nm-production-beijing-ramps-up-self-suffiency-2026-03-16/\n```\n\n**解决方案：**\n1. **优先使用 web_search (Tavily)** - 返回的链接是真实 URL\n2. **如果使用百度搜索** - 需要用 web_fetch 访问跳转链接获取真实 URL\n3. **验证链接** - 确保链接是可直接访问的完整域名\n\n**代码示例：**\n```javascript\n// 方法1: 使用 Tavily 搜索（推荐）\nweb_search({ query: \"新闻关键词\" })\n// 返回的 url 是真实链接，可直接使用\n\n// 方法2: 如果从百度搜索获取\n// 需要额外处理跳转链接\nconst realUrl = await web_fetch(baiduLink).finalUrl\n```\n\n---\n\n#### ✅ 正确的 Cron 任务指令模板","oldText":"🔗 来源：腾讯新闻 | https://view.inews.qq.com/a/20260329A02RIQ00\n```\n\n---\n\n#### ✅ 正确的 Cron 任务指令模板"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":99930,"output":481,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100411,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774917570973,"responseId":"f42ad1a509fffdbf62dd39fc16c41752"}}
