lawhub.ai/koreal6803/finlab\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7a30e15c51914d45\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nUse when working with trading strategies, backtesting, stock data, FinLabDataFrame, factor analy... **FinLab is installed via uv** (requires >= 1.5.9):. `uv run --with \\\"finlab\\\" python3 script.py`. **API Token is set** (required - finlab will fail without it):. **If no token, use finlab's built-in login** (available in >= 1.5.9):. finlab.login() # Opens browser for Google OAuth, saves token automatically`. from finlab.backtest import sim. close = data.get(\\\"price:收盤價\\\"). vol = data.get(\\\"price:成交股數\\\"). pb = data.get(\\\"price_earning_ratio:股價淨值比\\\"). ### Step 1: Fetch Data. # Price data. close = data.get(\\\"price:收盤價\\\"). pe = data.get(\\\"price_earning_ratio:本益比\\\"). pb = data.get(\\\"price_earning_ratio:股價淨值比\\\"). price = data.get('price:收盤價'). See <data-reference.md> for complete data catalog. See <dataframe-reference.md> for all FinLabDataFrame methods. position = entries.hold_until(exits, nstocks_limit=10, rank=-pb)`. `from finlab.backtest import sim. print(f\\\"Sharpe Ratio: {report.metrics.sharpe_ratio():.2f}\\\"). See <backtesting-reference.md> for complete `sim()` API. `from finlab.online.order_executor import Position, OrderExecutor. See <trading-reference.md> for complete broker setup and OrderExecutor API. | <data-reference.md> | `data.get()`, `data.universe()`, 900+ 欄位 |. | <backtesting-reference.md> | `sim()` 參數、stop-loss、rebalancing |. | <trading-reference.md> | 券商設定、OrderExecutor、Position |. | <dataframe-reference.md> | FinLabDataFrame 方法 |.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7a30e15c51914d45\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.99980897\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f5a32ca32796f66f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPtrade - ClawHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f5a32ca32796f66f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://clawhub.ai/cod