for Google OAuth, saves token automatically`. from finlab.backtest import sim. close = data.get(\"price:收盤價\"). vol = data.get(\"price:成交股數\"). pb = data.get(\"price_earning_ratio:股價淨值比\"). ### Step 1: Fetch Data. # Price data. close = data.get(\"price:收盤價\"). pe = data.get(\"price_earning_ratio:本益比\"). pb = data.get(\"price_earning_ratio:股價淨值比\"). price = data.get('price:收盤價'). See <data-reference.md> for complete data catalog. See <dataframe-reference.md> for all FinLabDataFrame methods. position = entries.hold_until(exits, nstocks_limit=10, rank=-pb)`. `from finlab.backtest import sim. print(f\"Sharpe Ratio: {report.metrics.sharpe_ratio():.2f}\"). See <backtesting-reference.md> for complete `sim()` API. `from finlab.online.order_executor import Position, OrderExecutor. See <trading-reference.md> for complete broker setup and OrderExecutor API. | <data-reference.md> | `data.get()`, `data.universe()`, 900+ 欄位 |. | <backtesting-reference.md> | `sim()` 參數、stop-loss、rebalancing |. | <trading-reference.md> | 券商設定、OrderExecutor、Position |. | <dataframe-reference.md> | FinLabDataFrame 方法 |.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7a30e15c51914d45\">>>","score":0.99980897},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f5a32ca32796f66f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPtrade - ClawHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f5a32ca32796f66f\">>>","url":"https://clawhub.ai/coderwpf/ptrade","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ad0898880b1bb1ed\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\ncurrent_price = data[g.security]['close']. log.info(f'{stock}: {price}, upper_limit={tick[\"up_px\"]}, lower_limit={tick[\"down_px\"]}'). order_list is a list of dicts containing: entrust_no, stock_code, amount, price,. log.info(f'Order {o[\"stock_code\"]}: status={o[\"status\"]}, filled={o[\"business_amount\"]}/{o[\"amount\"]}'). log.info(f'{direction} {t[\"stock_code\"]}: {t[\"business_amount\"]}@{t[\"business_price\"]}')`. `order(security, amount, limit_price=None). order('600570.SS', 100, li