{"type":"message","id":"778458d1","parentId":"8cbb5fac","timestamp":"2026-03-31T02:34:43.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"消息工具需要指定 channel，但当前没有检测到配置的通道。这很奇怪，因为飞书通道是启用状态的。\n\n让我检查一下如何发送消息...实际上，从之前的会话历史中，我看到飞书消息是通过某种方式发送的。让我检查一下会话配置。\n\n从 openclaw status 输出中，我看到飞书通道是 ON 状态：\n```\n| Feishu   | ON      | OK     | configured · accounts 9/9                                                              |\n```\n\n所以飞书通道是配置好的。问题可能是我需要使用正确的参数格式。\n\n让我尝试使用不同的参数...","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_31efba42d9b04edcb4fbe44f","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"~/.openclaw/skills/slack/SKILL.md","limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":68314,"output":283,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68597,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774924436549,"responseId":"6b3ea442f22696684529886d2689a6b4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fcc0f9db","parentId":"778458d1","timestamp":"2026-03-31T02:34:43.275Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_31efba42d9b04edcb4fbe44f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: slack\ndescription: Use when you need to control Slack from Clawdbot via the slack tool, including reacting to messages or pinning/unpinning items in Slack channels or DMs.\n---\n\n# Slack Actions\n\n## Overview\n\nUse `slack` to react, manage pins, send/edit/delete messages, and fetch member info. The tool uses the bot token configured for Clawdbot.\n\n## Inputs to collect\n\n- `channelId` and `messageId` (Slack message timestamp, e.g. `1712023032.1234`).\n- For reactions, an `emoji` (Unicode or `:name:`).\n- For message sends, a `to` target (`channel:<id>` or `user:<id>`) and `content`.\n\nMessage context lines include `slack message id` and `channel` fields you can reuse directly.\n\n## Actions\n\n### Action groups\n\n| Action group | Default | Notes |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| reactions | enabled | React + list reactions |\n| messages | enabled | Read/send/edit/delete |\n| pins | enabled | Pin/unpin/list |\n| memberInfo | enabled | Member info |\n| emojiList | enabled | Custom emoji list |\n\n### React to a message\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"react\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\",\n  \"emoji\": \"✅\"\n}\n```\n\n### List reactions\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"reactions\",\n  \"channelId\": \"C123\",\n  \"messageId\": \"1712023032.1234\"\n}\n\n[94 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774924483273}}
{"type":"message","id":"308cdc3f","parentId":"fcc0f9db","timestamp":"2026-03-31T02:35:16.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是 Slack 的技能文档，不是飞书的。让我检查飞书消息的发送方式。\n\n实际上，从会话历史中，我看到消息是直接发送的，不需要使用 message 工具。回复会自动发送到正确的通道。\n\n让我直接回复用户，内容会自动发送到飞书。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，创建飞书文档遇到了一些技术问题。让我把完整内容直接发送给您：\n\n---\n\n## 📊 股票量化分析与交易技能推荐\n\n> 搜索日期：2026年3月31日  \n> 来源平台：ClawHub + 腾讯技能中心\n\n---\n\n## 🏆 推荐技能 TOP 4\n\n### 1. Stock Copilot Pro ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\n**链接：** https://clawhub.ai/buxibuxi/stock-copilot-pro\n\n**功能特点：**\n- 🌍 全球市场（美股、港股、A股）\n- 📈 多维分析（基本面、技术面、情绪面）\n- 🔍 单股分析 + 多股比较\n- 👀 自选股/持仓管理\n- 📰 早晚报、行业雷达\n\n**使用示例：**\n```bash\nnode scripts/stock_copilot_pro.mjs analyze --symbol AAPL --market US\nnode scripts/stock_copilot_pro.mjs brief --type morning --format chat\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. FinLab ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\n**链接：** https://clawhub.ai/koreal6803/finlab\n\n**功能特点：**\n- 📊 台湾股市量化框架\n- 🧪 完整回测引擎\n- 📉 风险控制（止损/止盈/移动止损）\n- 🤖 券商对接自动交易\n\n**策略示例：**\n```python\nfrom finlab import data\nfrom finlab.backtest import sim\n\nclose = data.get(\"price:收盤價\")\npb = data.get(\"price_earning_ratio:股價淨值比\")\nposition = close.rise(10) & (close > close.average(60))\nreport = sim(position, resample=\"M\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Backtest Expert ⭐⭐⭐⭐\n**链接：** https://clawhub.ai/veeramanikandanr48/backtest-expert\n\n**核心理念：**\n> \"找到'最不容易失败'的策略，而不是'纸上利润最高'的策略\"\n\n**功能：**\n- 🎯 专业回测方法论\n- 🔍 压力测试、参数敏感性\n- ⚠️ 常见陷阱检测（前视偏差、生存偏差）\n\n---\n\n### 4. Ptrade ⭐⭐⭐⭐\n**链接：** https://clawhub.ai/coderwpf/ptrade\n\n**功能：**\n- 🔄 A股实盘自动下单\n- 💰 融资融券支持\n- ⏰ 盘后固定价格交易\n\n---\n\n## 📦 其他相关技能\n\n| 技能 | 用途 | 链接 |\n|------|------|------|\n| StockAPI | 量化数据接口 | https://www.skillsbot.cn/skill/8610 |\n| MarketPulse | 实时行情 | https://www.skillsbot.cn/skill/575 |\n| HFT Quant Expert | 高频量化 | https://www.skillsbot.cn/skill/4174 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 推荐组合\n\n| 场景 | 推荐技能 |\n|------|----------|\n| 日常投资分析 | Stock Copilot Pro |\n| 量化策略开发 | FinLab |\n| 策略验证 | Backtest Expert |\n| 实盘交易 | Ptrade |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 重要提示\n\n1. **不要让 AI 直接下单** - OpenClaw 作为信号生成器，人工决策\n2. **回测不能代表未来** - 即使通过压力测试的策略也可能失败\n3. **小资金验证** - 先用小资金测试，再逐步放大\n\n---\n\n📁 详细内容已保存至本地文件：\n`C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\股票量化分析与交易技能推荐.md`\n\n需要我帮您安装某个技能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":68826,"output":970,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774924483276,"responseId":"368d90a50795e9961bdccebc8fdfada4"}}
