{"type":"message","id":"4442d311","parentId":"234c4e69","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:16:45.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"firecrawl-cli 没有在这个目录下。可能之前的安装被覆盖或者没有保存。但用户现在要求安装 firecrawl-search，已经完成了。让我给用户一个清晰的回复。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Firecrawl Search 技能安装成功！**\n\n**安装位置：** `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\skills\\firecrawl-search`\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 主要功能\n\n| 命令 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `firecrawl_search \"query\"` | 网页搜索 |\n| `firecrawl_scrape \"url\"` | 抓取单个页面 |\n| `firecrawl_crawl \"url\"` | 爬取整个网站 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 配置 API Key\n\n```bash\n$env:FIRECRAWL_API_KEY = \"fc-YOUR-KEY\"\n```\n\n获取 API Key：https://www.firecrawl.dev/\n\n---\n\n需要我帮您安装其他 Firecrawl 相关技能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":93801,"output":238,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774973792616,"responseId":"951a7626caa752baa046f9bc169cb7d1"}}
